To build these tools you will need libbitcoin, and obelisk.

libbitcoin:

  https://github.com/spesmilo/libbitcoin

Follow the instructions in the libbitcoin README to install it.

Obelisk:

  https://github.com/genjix/obelisk

  $ git clone https://github.com/genjix/obelisk.git
  $ sudo apt-get install libzmq-dev libconfig++-dev
  $ make
  $ sudo make install

Now run the commands here:

  $ cd sx/src/extra
  $ make
  $ sudo make install

Edit the file /etc/sx.cfg to point to my server. It might be offline so
no promises. I'm planning a more persistent one later.

  $ vi /etc/sx.cfg

  service = "tcp://46.4.92.107:9091"

